name: WarpyWarp
description:
/!\ Made for the Weekly Game Jam 173: Secret door

W, A, S, D to move,
SPACE to jump,
F to interact

In this game you will need to warp between zones and assemble the warp by putting yourself in front of it to warp to the new zone.
 The game is rather short but we had fun experimenting new mechanics.
